briefTitle: Effect of Interval Cancer and Screening Process on Survival and Disease-free Period in Breast Cancer
officialTitle: CAMISS Retrospective Cohort - Effect of Interval Cancer and Screening Process on Survival and Disease-free Period in Breast Cancer
eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* Women aged between 50 to 69 years with invasive or in situ breast cancer.

Exclusion Criteria:

* Women diagnosed with lobular carcinoma in situ.
